---
title: Aegean Sea-Inspired Feta Meatballs with Lemon-Pepper Potatoes and Garlic-Feta Sauce
description: Feta cheese is the secret ingredient for giving juicy DIY meatballs a briny, salty pop! Complete this Greek-inspired feast with garlic potatoes and a fresh side salad that will please the whole family.
